{"title":"廵哨","authors":["陈思民"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":4,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"廵哨（快板）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"福建南通公社罗洲大队民兵　陈思民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更深人静月正高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田野茫茫夜雾罩；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转出村头轻步走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我跟班长去巡哨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"班长一声口令传，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我俩同时来卧倒："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我问班长为啥事？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"班长只把手来摇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大树后面有人影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是民兵在放哨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细看值勤是谁人？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"班长的爱人桂花嫂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我嘴里不说心里笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"班长的眼力没我高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明明是个自己人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么看成是目标。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我再把眼睛向前瞧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咦！？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么人影没处找。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我向班长作报告，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"班长说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我们的目标暴露了！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不见来人声先到："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“什么人？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口音宏亮音调高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“自己人！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我赶紧回答把名报。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“回令！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“山鹰！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“回令！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“夜猫！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哎呀！原来真是桂花嫂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桂花嫂过来埋怨道："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你们呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为啥跟我来胡闹？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"班长连忙作回答："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我们来把你考一考。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“哼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要答不上口令不客气！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“哼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要是麻痹叫你作检讨！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说了一席正经话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不禁各人都发笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最后大家表态度："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“有我们这一双夜猫眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人一个跑不掉！”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}